I have enough context to write the verifier. The implementation is going to use the exact vulnerable transfer path on the live HODL token, keep pre-sell fee-bucket volume below the token’s `4,000 HODL` auto-swap threshold, and isolate the flash-funded attempt in a child contract so an economically failing route reports cleanly instead of reverting the harness.
